# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok joe nathan left the bases loaded in the final two innings for his ##rd save and the minnesota twins held on sunday for an ##-# victory over the seattle mariners .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (l / leave-14
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Joe"
                        :op2 "Nathan"))
            :ARG1 (b / base
                  :ARG1-of (l2 / load-01))
            :time (f / final
                  :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 2
                        :unit (m / minute)))
            :purpose (s / save-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                        :value 3)))
      :op2 (h / hold-04
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :quant 2
                  :mod (s2 / state
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Minneapolis"))
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Minister"))
                        :ARG2 (t2 / twin)))
            :ARG1 (w / win-01
                  :ARG0 p2
                  :ARG1 (t3 / team
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Seahiner")))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s3 / sunday))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :mod (s / state
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Georgia")))
                  :ARG1 (c / chance-02
                        :ARG0 ii
                        :ARG1 (p / prove-01
                              :ARG0 ii
                              :ARG1 (o / owe-01
                                    :ARG0 (s2 / state)
                                    :ARG1 (d / damages-02)
                                    :ARG2 ii
                                    :ARG3 (a / accommodate-01
                                          :polarity -
                                          :ARG0 s2
                                          :ARG1 (d2 / disability
                                                :poss ii))))
                        :ARG1-of (f / fresh-04))))
      :mod (u / unanimous)
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

                  :dayperiod (m4 / morning))
            :mod (c3 / continent
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Europe"))))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :name (n2 / name

                  :ARG0-of (c3 / combine-01
                        :ARG1 (ii / image
                              :ARG1-of (p3 / pure-02))
                        :ARG2 (c4 / color
                              :mod (c5 / cheery))
                        :ARG3 (h / humor
                              :ARG0-of (e / engage-01))
                        :purpose (a2 / advertise-01
                              :ARG0 p
                              :ARG1 (p4 / product
                                    :ARG1-of (r / range-01
                                          :ARG3 (c6 / car)
                                          :ARG4 (a3 / aspirin)
                                          :ARG4 (s / shampoo))))))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (m / monday))
            :location (h2 / home
                  :location (c7 / city
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Istanbul")
                        :location c))))

# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (m / military)
      :ARG1 (c / curfews)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday))
      :location (t / town
            :quant 7
            :location (v / valley
                  :ARG1-of (s / swat-01)))
      :ARG0-of (s2 / signal-07
            :ARG1 (c2 / confident-01
                  :ARG2 (p / progress-01
                        :ARG1 (o / offense-02
                              :ARG0 (m3 / military)
                              :ARG1 (c3 / criminal-organization
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Taliban"))
                              :location (t2 / there))))
            :mod (f / further))
      :concession (f2 / flare-02
            :ARG1 (v2 / violence)
            :location (e / elsewhere)))

                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Malaysia"))
                  :ARG2 (m / minister
                        :mod (p2 / prime))))
      :ARG1 (p3 / person
            :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c2 / coalition
                        :mod (f / front
                              :mod (n4 / nation))
                        :ARG0-of (r / rule-03))
                  :ARG2 (m2 / member)))
      :ARG2 (a / and
            :op1 (r2 / ready-02
                  :ARG1 p3
                  :ARG2 (e / elect-01
                        :ARG1-of (s / snap-04)
                        :ARG1-of (g / general-02)))
            :op2 (s2 / strive-01
                  :ARG0 p3
                  :ARG1 (w / win-01
                        :ARG0 p3)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :dayperiod (s3 / sunday)))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Jean-pierre"
                  :op2 " escalettes")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (f / federation
                        :poss (c / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "France")))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (c2 / confirm-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Raymond"
                              :op2 " domenech")
                        :ARG0-of (c3 / coach-01
                              :ARG1 c))
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (f2 / friday)))
            :op2 (l / lead-02
                  :ARG0 p3
                  :ARG1 (t / team
                        :poss p3)
                  :ARG2 (g / game
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "World"
                              :op2 "Cup")
                        :location (c4 / continent
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "South"
                                    :op2 "Africa"))
                        :time (y / year
                              :mod (n6 / next))))))

      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / police)
      :ARG1 (l / lock-01
            :ARG0 (c / couple
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Palestine")))
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                              :ARG1 c
                              :ARG2 (s2 / son))
                        :ARG1-of (d / disable-01))
                  :op2 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                              :ARG1 c
                              :ARG2 (d2 / daughter))))
            :ARG2 (r / room
                  :quant 2
                  :ARG0-of (s3 / stink-01))
            :duration (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 4
                  :unit (d3 / decade))
            :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (f / fear-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG1 (r2 / ruin-01
                              :ARG0 c
                              :ARG1 (p4 / prospect-02
                                    :ARG0 c
                                    :ARG1 (m / marry-01
                                          :ARG1 c)
                                    :condition (d4 / discover-01
                                          :ARG1 c))))))
      :time (w / wednesday))
